def print_poem():
    poem = [
        "Ride of the Soul\n",
        "\n",
        "In the twilight where the road unfurls,\n",
        "Where the sky turns shades of burnt amber,\n",
        "I find myself drawn to the whispering curves,\n",
        "Of asphalt dreams and moonlit wonder.\n",
        "\n",
        "With the engine’s purr as my constant guide,\n",
        "I set forth on this endless quest,\n",
        "Across the highway of the heart,\n",
        "Where freedom and fate coalesce.\n",
        "\n",
        "The sun dips low, casting its golden hue,\n",
        "Across the desert’s rolling expanse,\n",
        "I feel the pull of the open sky,\n",
        "In the symphony of the wind’s romance.\n",
        "\n",
        "The city lights behind me fade,\n",
        "A distant memory of a life once known,\n",
        "Now, the stars become my companions,\n",
        "In a universe where I roam alone.\n",
        "\n",
        "Each mile a step away from the past,\n",
        "From echoes of chains that held me tight,\n",
        "I shed the weight of yesterday’s ghosts,\n",
        "In the embrace of the star-filled night.\n",
        "\n",
        "In the rearview, I see reflections,\n",
        "Of roads and faces I left behind,\n",
        "Yet, ahead, the horizon promises,\n",
        "A path where my true self I’ll find.\n",
        "\n",
        "I ride with the rhythm of the open road,\n",
        "Feeling the pulse of life’s sweet song,\n",
        "A melody of dreams and desires,\n",
        "In which my restless heart belongs.\n",
        "\n",
        "The moon, a silent witness to my journey,\n",
        "Lights the way with a silvery grace,\n",
        "Guiding me through the vast unknown,\n",
        "To a place where I’ll find my place.\n",
        "\n",
        "Beneath the canopy of endless stars,\n",
        "I dance with shadows and fleeting light,\n",
        "In the quiet moments between the beats,\n",
        "I’m both the wanderer and the night.\n",
        "\n",
        "The road stretches like an endless promise,\n",
        "Beneath the canopy of dreams unbound,\n",
        "With every turn, I hear the echoes,\n",
        "Of a heart that yearns and is found.\n",
        "\n",
        "In the solitude of this midnight ride,\n",
        "I discover the essence of my soul,\n",
        "The freedom I sought in the distant haze,\n",
        "Now a reality, making me whole.\n",
        "\n",
        "The road sings a song of liberation,\n",
        "In its twists and turns, I find my way,\n",
        "Every mile a verse of my existence,\n",
        "Every breath a line of the day.\n",
        "\n",
        "And as the dawn begins to break,\n",
        "The horizon blushes with morning light,\n",
        "I know that this journey of the soul,\n",
        "Has brought me closer to what’s right.\n",
        "\n",
        "For in the endless road beneath me,\n",
        "I’ve found a place where I am free,\n",
        "A rider of the wind and dreams,\n",
        "In search of my own destiny.\n",
        "\n",
        "With each new sunrise, I embrace,\n",
        "The beauty of a world unchained,\n",
        "In the ride of the soul, I find my grace,\n",
        "In the journey that remains unfeigned.\n"
    ]
    
    # Print each line of the poem
    for line in poem:
        print(line, end='')

# Call the function to print the poem
print_poem()